          4. Embrace White Space
        </h2>
        <p class="article-content__text">
        White space, or negative space, is a powerful tool in
         typography. It helps in decluttering designs and allows
          each typographic element to breathe. Proper use of 
          white space can significantly improve the overall 
          balance and composition of your design.
